{"tid":286561,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"蝙蝠俠仆街","createTime":"2017-06-16T16:41:45.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-16T17:40:35.000Z","uid":86102,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"79bd8fe1574bc9061a6fd09a59a08c292d8dc940","tid":286561,"uid":86102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T16:41:45.000Z","msg":"我啱一打開門見到有隻黑色物體<br />\n原來係隻可愛蝙蝠仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但佢好似受左傷飛唔到 只可以爬下爬下 <br />\n而家腳繞住地拖<br />\n請問我應該點做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我又驚唔敢掂佢<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/17/003938_6881d0c82da97a80d2d0e0671a7f3258.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F17%2F003938_6881d0c82da97a80d2d0e0671a7f3258.jpg&h=1af7ac04&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e623a4f1108c39989cdb6271592e5d9085e4a7e3","tid":286561,"uid":693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T16:43:45.000Z","msg":"連登仔勁到蝙蝠都執到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6ef919e191d11a1406d05fa4732d585d03e0ecd","tid":286561,"uid":18917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T16:45:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"df7103c6ad692fa7f1cc5f808613ff865dfe9ad4","tid":286561,"uid":89182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T16:45:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/17/004542_62cb9eaa1f837ebc2028770e9b712e90.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F17%2F004542_62cb9eaa1f837ebc2028770e9b712e90.jpg&h=a33d5c2d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5055bfa3b5c4d54dd85e133cb0f65d66d8fb0315","tid":286561,"uid":3549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T16:48:04.000Z","msg":"我諗遲下穿山甲都有連登仔執到<img src=\"/asset